summary: An ordinance relating to the design and construction of a portion of a limited access arterial highway improvement on S.W. Spokane Street from Iowa Ave. S.W. to 36th Ave. S.W. in the vicinity of Avalon Way S.W. under Ordinance 90448, and amending Section 2 of said Ordinance to provide that payments for such improvement shall be from the Arterial City Street Fund.
